OL,3,CFormer Spandau Ballet singer found
OL,4,Cguilty of rape
OL,6,FA former Spandau Ballet singer has
OL,7,Fbeen found guilty of rape and
OL,8,Fattempted rape.
OL,10,FRoss Davidson was known for singing
OL,11,Fwith the 80s band, and had starred in
OL,12,F'We Will Rock You'- a West End show
OL,13,Ffeaturing some of Queen's biggest hits.
OL,15,FThe performer from Finchley, North
OL,16,FLondon had pleaded not guilty to the
OL,17,Frape of a woman in London, in March
OL,18,F2015, along with the attempted rape
OL,19,Fand sexual assault of another woman in
OL,20,FThailand, in December 2019, saying his
OL,21,Factions were consensual.
