OL,3,CFormer Spandau Ballet singer found
OL,4,Cguilty of rape
OL,6,FAfter more than eleven hours of
OL,7,Fdeliberation, jurors found him guilty
OL,8,Fof all charges.
OL,10,FDuring the trial, Prosecutor Richard
OL,11,FHearnden said Davidson had been
OL,12,Fthought of as "a bit of a sex symbol"
OL,13,Fbut the two women say he had "a much
OL,14,Fdarker side that they did not notice,
OL,15,Fat least at first."
