OL,3,CFormer Spandau Ballet singer found
OL,4,Cguilty of rape
OL,6,FHe had success, musical talent and was
OL,7,Fconsidered "charming and charismatic"
OL,8,Fbut "it is because Ross Davidson
OL,9,Fexpects to get sex on demand that he
OL,10,Fwill resort to rape and sexual assault
OL,11,Fif he is not given what he thinks he
OL,12,Fdeserves", Mr Hearnden said.
OL,14,FThe rape victim said she was attacked
OL,15,Fin her sleep, and left feeling
OL,16,F"helpless" and "scared to react".
OL,18,FDavidson, who met the women on the
OL,19,Fdating app Tinder, said that all sex
OL,20,Fhe had was consensual.
